description:
Tackle steep switchbacks on a day hike or wear these for a multi-day trip. These pants roll up to capri length for sunny days. Internal drawcord and belt loops let you tune the fit in the waist. Gusseted crotch and articulated knees add range of motion for getting over obstacles on the trail. Fabric dries out quickly, in case creek crossings don’t go quite as planned.Made of a stretchy, quick-drying nylon and spandex blend with a DWR (durable water repellent) finish to shed water and dirt.Fabric provides a UPF 50+ rating.Zipper fly with button closure.Side zippered pocket on seam and zippered back pockets to keep your stuff safe when you're active.Roll up the hem and convert them to capris with the inner buttons and fabric tabs and outer loops.Straight leg openings.Machine wash cold. Do not bleach. Tumble dry low. Iron low when needed. Do not dry clean.

